{"data": [{"id": "4741607", "title": "Workday: Lower Growth Expectation, But Upside Is Still Attractive", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148703154/image_2148703154.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Business persons on meeting in the office.\" data-id=\"2148703154\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"912px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148703154/image_2148703154.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148703154/image_2148703154.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148703154/image_2148703154.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148703154/image_2148703154.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148703154/image_2148703154.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148703154/image_2148703154.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148703154/image_2148703154.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148703154/image_2148703154.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">VioletaStoimenova</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Summary</h2> <p>Following <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4722834-workday-stock-multiple-growth-opportunities-ahead\">my coverage</a> on Workday (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/WDAY\" title=\"Workday, Inc.\">WDAY</a></span>) in Sep\u201924, which I recommended a buy rating due to my expectation that growth could accelerate to 20%, this post is to provide an update on my thoughts on the business</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148703154/image_2148703154.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741607-workday-lower-growth-expectation-but-upside-is-still-attractive", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 02:27:39"}, {"id": "4741609", "title": "Zscaler, Inc. 2025 Q1 - Results - Earnings Call Presentation", "description": "<p>The following slide deck was published by Zscaler, Inc. in conjunction with their 2025 Q1 earnings call.</p> <p><figure class=\"sa-presentation paywall-full-content invisible\" data-id=\"105995\"></figure></p>", "image": null, "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741609-zscaler-inc-2025-q1-results-earnings-call-presentation", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 02:21:17"}, {"id": "4741606", "title": "Trump Begins To Create His Future", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/856858944/image_856858944.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Businessman pointing CREATE YOUR FUTURE! word on blackboard\" data-id=\"856858944\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/856858944/image_856858944.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/856858944/image_856858944.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/856858944/image_856858944.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/856858944/image_856858944.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/856858944/image_856858944.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/856858944/image_856858944.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/856858944/image_856858944.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/856858944/image_856858944.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">relif/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>\"Despite a furor set off by President-elect Donald J. Trump's latest pronouncements about tariffs and immigration, the stock market resumed its upward surge in holiday-shortened trading on Friday, propelling the benchmark S&amp;P 500 to its best monthly gain</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/856858944/image_856858944.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741606-mr-trump-begins-to-create-his-future", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 02:19:20"}, {"id": "4741608", "title": "CleanSpark, Inc. 2024 Q4 - Results - Earnings Call Presentation", "description": "<p>The following slide deck was published by CleanSpark, Inc. in conjunction with their 2024 Q4 earnings call.</p> <p><figure class=\"sa-presentation paywall-full-content invisible\" data-id=\"105994\"></figure></p>", "image": null, "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741608-cleanspark-inc-2024-q4-results-earnings-call-presentation", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 02:15:28"}, {"id": "4741603", "title": "Quaker Chemical: Positioning Concerns", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1412857430/image_1412857430.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Glass molecular structure\" data-id=\"1412857430\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1229px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1412857430/image_1412857430.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1412857430/image_1412857430.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1412857430/image_1412857430.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1412857430/image_1412857430.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1412857430/image_1412857430.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1412857430/image_1412857430.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1412857430/image_1412857430.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1412857430/image_1412857430.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Jonathan Kitchen</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>In the summer of 2023 I believed that <strong>Quaker Chemical (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/KWR\" title=\"Quaker Chemical Corporation\">KWR</a></span>)</strong> was offering a mixed bag for investors. While I believed that more earnings upside was seen, the company has only been posting flattish earnings amidst falling sales here, due</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1412857430/image_1412857430.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741603-quaker-chemical-positioning-concerns", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 02:05:47"}, {"id": "4741432", "title": "Omega Healthcare: Back To Pre-Pandemic Levels, But I Think It Consolidates (Rating Downgrade)", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810162/image_1445810162.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Money growth\" data-id=\"1445810162\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1055px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810162/image_1445810162.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810162/image_1445810162.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810162/image_1445810162.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810162/image_1445810162.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810162/image_1445810162.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810162/image_1445810162.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810162/image_1445810162.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810162/image_1445810162.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">PM Images</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>It\u2019s been a satisfying year for Omega Healthcare Investors (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/OHI\" title=\"Omega Healthcare Investors, Inc.\">OHI</a></span>) investors as shares have appreciated by over 30%, causing them to settle above $40 and reach their pre-pandemic levels. I remained bullish on OHI during the pandemic while shares hovered around the $30</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810162/image_1445810162.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741432-omega-healthcare-back-to-pre-pandemic-levels-but-i-think-it-consolidates-rating-downgrade", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 02:00:00"}, {"id": "4741601", "title": "SIGA Technologies Vs Emergent BioSolutions: Product Portfolio And Future Outlook", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1211986569/image_1211986569.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Female doctor prohibiting access to a restricted area\" data-id=\"1211986569\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"567px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1211986569/image_1211986569.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1211986569/image_1211986569.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1211986569/image_1211986569.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1211986569/image_1211986569.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1211986569/image_1211986569.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1211986569/image_1211986569.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1211986569/image_1211986569.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1211986569/image_1211986569.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">doble-d/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Thesis</h2> <p><b>SIGA Technologies, Inc.</b> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SIGA\" title=\"SIGA Technologies, Inc.\">SIGA</a></span>) (\u201cSiga\u201d) is a pharmaceutical company focused on developing and commercializing therapeutics for the prevention or treatment of infectious diseases. Their lead product is <a href=\"https://www.siga.com/tpoxx\" rel=\"nofollow\">TPOXX</a> (Tecovirimat), an antiviral treatment</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1211986569/image_1211986569.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741601-siga-technologies-vs-emergent-biosolutions-product-portfolio-and-future-outlook", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 01:49:22"}, {"id": "4741599", "title": "KE Holdings: Upside Is Attractive, But I Prefer To Wait For More Proof", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1500297506/image_1500297506.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Aerial view over houses in Paris suburb\" data-id=\"1500297506\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1152px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1500297506/image_1500297506.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1500297506/image_1500297506.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1500297506/image_1500297506.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1500297506/image_1500297506.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1500297506/image_1500297506.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1500297506/image_1500297506.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1500297506/image_1500297506.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1500297506/image_1500297506.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Gary Yeowell</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Investment overview</h2> <p>I give a hold rating for KE Holdings (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/BEKE\" title=\"KE Holdings Inc.\">BEKE</a></span>) as I await more proof that the current demand improvement trend is sustainable. Specifically, I would need to see growth acceleration, backed by improving demand at the macro</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1500297506/image_1500297506.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741599-ke-holdings-stock-attractive-upside-but-prefer-to-await-more-proof", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 01:45:22"}, {"id": "4741598", "title": "FS KKR Capital: A 13% Yield And Repricing Upside", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155095389/image_155095389.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Yield Road Sign Post Over a Blue Sky\" data-id=\"155095389\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"5600px\" height=\"3743px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155095389/image_155095389.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155095389/image_155095389.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155095389/image_155095389.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155095389/image_155095389.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155095389/image_155095389.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155095389/image_155095389.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155095389/image_155095389.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155095389/image_155095389.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">ryasick</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>FS KKR Capital (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/FSK\" title=\"FS KKR Capital Corp\">FSK</a></span>) has seen a consistent narrowing of the gap between share price and net asset value in the second half of 2024 which is a result of the BDC improving its balance sheet quality</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155095389/image_155095389.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741598-fs-kkr-capital-a-13-percent-yield-and-repricing-upside", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 01:38:37"}, {"id": "4741596", "title": "Global-E Online Ltd.: Positive Demand Environment Should Enable Growth Acceleration", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1744124538/image_1744124538.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Woman purchasing clothes on a mobile app\" data-id=\"1744124538\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1744124538/image_1744124538.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1744124538/image_1744124538.jpg?io=getty-c-w12